---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Energy Prices By State | Surging Residential Costs"
    description="Explore the rapid growth of residential electricity and methane gas prices across the U.S. from 2019 to 2024, and why efficient infrastructure is critical."
>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <header class="relative pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-32 overflow-hidden bg-slate-900 border-b border-tech-blue/20">
        <!-- Abstract gradient background -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-tech-blue/20 via-slate-900 to-texas-pine/20 z-0"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-full h-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-tech-blue/10 via-transparent to-transparent z-0"></div>
        
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
            <div class="max-w-3xl">
                <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-tech-blue/20 text-blue-200 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-6 border border-tech-blue/30 backdrop-blur-sm">National Analysis</span>
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-6">
                    Where is energy getting the <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-brand-green">most expensive?</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed font-light mb-8 max-w-2xl">
                    Across the U.S., households are struggling to afford rapidly rising electricity and methane gas bills. From 2019 to 2024, average residential electricity prices rose significantly faster than the cumulative inflation rate, squeezing families nationwide.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50 relative">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            
            <!-- Map Visualization -->
            <div class="mb-24">
                <div class="text-center mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-4">The Price Hike Landscape</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">This map illustrates the state-by-state differences in electricity price growth over a five-year window (2019-2024), revealing distinct regional crises.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-4 md:p-8 shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/50 border border-slate-200 mx-auto max-w-5xl group overflow-hidden relative">
                    <!-- Subtle glow effect behind the map container -->
                    <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-tech-blue to-texas-pine rounded-3xl blur opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-20 transition duration-1000"></div>
                    <img 
                        src="/energy-map.jpg" 
                        alt="Map showing the growth in residential electricity prices across the United States from 2019 to 2024" 
                        class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl relative z-10"
                    />
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Core Drivers Grid -->
            <div class="mb-24">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-10 text-center">Core Drivers of Rising Rates</h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <!-- Driver 1 -->
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-tech-blue/30 transition-all duration-300 group relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-tech-blue scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-500 origin-left"></div>
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-orange-600">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="size-6">
                              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.362 5.214A8.252 8.252 0 0 1 12 21 8.25 8.25 0 0 1 6.038 7.047 8.287 8.287 0 0 0 9 9.601a8.983 8.983 0 0 1 3.361-6.866 8.21 8.21 0 0 0 3 2.48Z" />
                              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 18a3.75 3.75 0 0 0 .495-7.468 5.99 5.99 0 0 0-1.925 3.547 5.975 5.975 0 0 1-2.133-1.001A3.75 3.75 0 0 0 12 18Z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Wildfire Mitigation</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">In states like California, electricity bills are being driven up substantially by billions of dollars in essential but costly wildfire mitigation and prevention efforts.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Driver 2 -->
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-texas-pine/30 transition-all duration-300 group relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-texas-pine scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-500 origin-left"></div>
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-blue-600">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="size-6">
                              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 3v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 6 16.5h2.25M3.75 3h-1.5m1.5 0h16.5m0 0h1.5m-1.5 0v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 18 16.5h-2.25m-7.5 0h7.5m-7.5 0-1 3m8.5-3 1 3m0 0 .5 1.5m-.5-1.5h-9.5m0 0-.5 1.5m.75-9 3-3 2.148 2.148A12.061 12.061 0 0 1 16.5 7.605" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Peak Grid Demand</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Texas is struggling to meet its rapidly growing peak electricity demand during severe summer heatwaves, leading to aggressive capacity expansion costs.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Driver 3 -->
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-amber-400/30 transition-all duration-300 group relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-amber-400 scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-500 origin-left"></div>
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-amber-600">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="size-6">
                              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8.25M15.75 21v-8.25M8.25 21v-8.25M3 9l9-6 9 6m-1.5 12V10.332A48.36 48.36 0 0 0 12 9.75c-2.551 0-5.056.2-7.5.582V21M3 21h18M12 6.75h.008v.008H12V6.75Z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Aging Distribution</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Across the country, the primary cost isn't strictly generating electricity, but fixing the legacy systems that physically deliver it to households against extreme weather.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- The Methane Gas Reality -->
            <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden">
               <!-- Decorative Grid Pattern -->
               <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 2px 2px, white 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 32px 32px;"></div>
               
               <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-center">
                   <div class="md:w-2/3">
                       <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Methane Gas is Increasing Even Faster</h2>
                       <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                           The missing counterpart to the electric grid narrative is the dramatic growth in residential gas prices, which surged an astonishing <strong class="text-white">39%</strong> over this same five-year period.
                       </p>
                       <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed border-l-4 border-tech-blue pl-4">
                           Three-quarters of U.S. states have seen methane gas prices rise significantly faster than inflation, primarily due to delayed cost recoveries from winter price spikes and the immense cost of maintaining vast underground distribution networks.
                       </p>
                   </div>
                   <div class="md:w-1/3 flex justify-center">
                       <div class="w-48 h-48 rounded-full border-8 border-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center flex-col shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(10,54,157,0.3)] bg-slate-900 relative">
                           <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-tech-blue to-teal-400">39%</div>
                           <div class="text-sm tracking-widest text-slate-400 font-medium uppercase mt-2">Increase</div>
                           
                           <!-- Decorative orbital rings -->
                           <div class="absolute inset-[-12px] border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full animate-[spin_10s_linear_infinite]"></div>
                           <div class="absolute inset-[-24px] border border-tech-blue/10 rounded-full animate-[spin_15s_linear_infinite_reverse]"></div>
                       </div>
                   </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- CTA Section connecting it to AI/DCs -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white border-t border-slate-100">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Moving Toward Efficient Design</h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                As legacy systems face immense pricing pressures, developing highly-efficient, closed-loop infrastructure from the outset is no longer optional—it is the baseline for sustainable growth.
            </p>
            <a href="/advancing-mankind" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold rounded-full text-white bg-tech-blue hover:bg-tech-blue-dark transition-colors shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-0.5 transform duration-200">
                Explore the Solutions
                <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path>
                </svg>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
